name: sterling silver stamped stack rings
description: These are 5 stack rings that I hand filed, soldered and stamped. I can make these in any size that you would like and get them right out to you. I personally wear an exact set like these and I wear them everyday! They are the perfect everyday choice and are so comfortable that I forget they are even on. I am always getting compliments on them and I know that you will too! just send me a message in the paypal section for the size that you would like.

name: sterling silver sakura cherry blossom necklace
description: I made this cherry blossom necklace completely on accident and I could not be any happier with the way that it turned out. I lightly hammered the branches to give it a more realistic texture and then soldered on my silver cherry blossom flowers and gave them a light oxidation. The whole piece was tumbled for strength and polishing. I have it on a fully adjustable chain that can go from choker to almost 20" so its perfect for anyone.

name: sterling silver stamped i carry your heart bracelet
description:
I love love love this bracelet! It is based on the poem by e.e. cummings and I have printed it below for you just in case you do not know it or maybe just want to read it again as I so often do. I have cut, filed, stamped, soldered and oxidized this bracelet. I would be happy to stamp the name of you and your honey on the back at no extra charge. It has a small section of chain in between the two silver pieces and I have hung 2 swarovski dangles in the center and one from the end. It is fully adjustable so one size fits all. One of my favorite pieces by far.

name: sterling silver fleur de lis spiral notebook with chain
description:
This is such a pretty pendant! I have stamped the inside with a quote on friendship but you can have yours custom stamped with anything that you would like. (as long as its not much longer than the quote that I have here.) It is more rectangular in shape than my other square pendants and has a beautifully soldered fleur de lis on the front. It comes on a 16 or 18" chain..your choice.
send me an email if you would like to see how its stamped inside.

name: sterling silver pet tag dog or cat
description: I made this dog tag out of sterling silver. I stamped out the circle shape, filed it, drilled a hole and then soldered on a little paw print. I can stamp on your pooches name and your phone number on the front and if you would like, even your address on the back, or you can have a custom saying on the front like I have stamped. Just send me a message in the paypal section with the info you want and I will get it right out to you. This tag is roughly the size a quarter. I have put on a base metal split ring which is very durable!
